.TH snmpa_conf 3 "snmp 5.20.1" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
snmpa_conf \- Utility functions for handling the agent config files.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The module \fIsnmpa_conf\fR contains various utility functions to use for manipulating (write/read/append) the config files of the SNMP agent.

.SH DATA TYPES
.LP
.B
\fB-opaque agent_entry() \fR

.br
.RS
.PP
An opaque term that represents an entry in the 'agent' config.


.RE
.B
\fB-opaque community_entry() \fR

.br
.RS
.PP
An opaque term that represents an entry in the 'community' (agent) config.


.RE
