.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
.B
\fBagent_entry(Tag, Val) -> AgentEntry\fR
\fB                     when\fR
\fB                         Tag ::\fR
\fB                             intAgentTransports | intAgentUDPPort |\fR
\fB                             snmpEngineMaxMessageSize | snmpEngineID,\fR
\fB                         Val :: term(),\fR
\fB                         AgentEntry :: agent_entry().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Create an entry for the agent config file, \fIagent.conf\fR.

.PP
The type of \fIVal\fR depends on the value of \fITag\fR:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fB\fIintAgentTransports: \fR[\fIsnmpa_conf:intAgentTransport()\fR ] \fI<mandatory>\fR\fR

.RE


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fB\fIintAgentUDPPort: \fR\fIinet:port_number()\fR \fI<optional>\fR\fR

.RE


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fB\fIsnmpEngineMaxMessageSize: \fR\fIsnmp_framework_mib:max_message_size()\fR \fI<mandatory>\fR\fR

.RE


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fB\fIsnmpEngineID: \fR\fIsnmp_framework_mib:engine_id()\fR \fI<mandatory>\fR\fR

.RE

.PP
See Agent Information for more info.


